<p>Teamwork Commerce HQ is giving back in a meaningful way by partnering with several local schools in Clearwater. Ahead of the first day of classes, our team donated backpacks and essential school supplies to six lower-income schools to help students start the year with confidence.</p>
<p>This effort is part of our ongoing commitment to support and uplift the community we're proud to call home. Investing in these students isn't just a donation for us. It's a chance to pay it forward and make a real impact where it matters most.</p>
